OL,3,CExperts urge customers to seek best
OL,4,Csavings after Ofgem lowers price cap
OL,6,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,7,Fexplains what Ofgem's latest
OL,8,Fannouncement means for households
OL,10,FThe amount millions of people pay for
OL,11,Fenergy will get lower from April, but
OL,12,Fthere are warnings that to get the
OL,13,Fbiggest savings, customers may still
OL,14,Fneed to take action.
OL,16,FExperts fear that because bills are
OL,17,Fgoing down automatically in the
OL,18,Fspring, people won't bother to look at
OL,19,Fthe possibility of cutting their costs
OL,20,Fby shopping around.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
