OL,3,CExperts urge customers to seek best
OL,4,Csavings after Ofgem lowers price cap
OL,6,FThe energy watchdog, Ofgem, today said
OL,7,Fthere was a 20% rise in energy deal
OL,8,Fswitching last year. On average,
OL,9,Fpeople made annual savings of #115.
OL,11,FWhat's the best way to take advantage
OL,12,Fof the lower price cap?
OL,14,FITV News asked energy experts at
OL,15,FUswitch to gather the most up-to-date
OL,16,Fresearch.
OL,18,FWe've been told about 15 current fixed-
OL,19,Frate deals that beat the upcoming
OL,20,FApril price cap, with an average
OL,21,Fsaving of #63.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
