OL,3,CExperts urge customers to seek best
OL,4,Csavings after Ofgem lowers price cap
OL,6,FSome deals could save more than #140
OL,7,Foff the new price cap coming in April.
OL,9,FThirty-three million customers on
OL,10,Fprice-capped tariffs and 21 million on
OL,11,Ffixed rate deals should all see an
OL,12,Faverage saving of #117 a year from
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FThis is a result of government policy
OL,16,Fto take the cost of two big
OL,17,Fenvironmental schemes off our bills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
